<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 00:32:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列主要政治民意调查专家去世，享年 78 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-leading-political-pollster-dies-at-78/0000018e-a5db-dd6b-abae-f7db285f0000</link><description>卡米尔·福克斯是 Dialog 民意调查研究所的首席研究员，为媒体提供民意调查和选举样本。他在 2018 年表示，“如果你有求知欲，这就是世界上最有趣的工作”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 21:38:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-leading-political-pollster-dies-at-78/0000018e-a5db-dd6b-abae-f7db285f0000</guid></item><item><title>外国外交官表示，加沙援助人员被杀损害了粮食分配和对以色列国防军的信任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomats-say-killing-of-aid-workers-in-gaza-harms-food-distribution-trust-in-idf/0000018e-a56b-d24a-abbf-ef6ba2550000</link><description>一名外交官表示，“由于操作故障，向北迁移的援助人员受到了武装分子的威胁，现在显然也受到了以色列国防军的威胁”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 20:07:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomats-say-killing-of-aid-workers-in-gaza-harms-food-distribution-trust-in-idf/0000018e-a56b-d24a-abbf-ef6ba2550000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡家外抗议活动中发生的一起事件，搁置了 10 月 7 日的大屠杀和人质事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/one-incident-at-the-protest-outside-the-pms-home-erased-both-october-7-and-the-hostages/0000018e-a4f7-d24a-abbf-eefff1020000</link><description>如果类似的示威活动发生在一个独裁政权的国家，以色列人可能会同情抗议者，即使其中一些人采取暴力行动。 ■ 如果内塔尼亚胡拒绝甘茨9月份举行选举的提议，民族团结党可能会退出政府五月</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 19:38:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/one-incident-at-the-protest-outside-the-pms-home-erased-both-october-7-and-the-hostages/0000018e-a4f7-d24a-abbf-eefff1020000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨提议九月在以色列举行选举；内塔尼亚胡：政府将继续执政直至实现战争目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/gantz-proposes-election-in-september-pm-govt-will-continue-until-war-goals-are-achieved/0000018e-a53b-df61-a1ef-ef7be5b20000</link><description>在周三的新闻发布会上，甘茨表示，他希望“所有负责任的公共领导人都加入联合政府”，随后内塔尼亚胡指责部长在战时处理“小政治”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 19:18:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/gantz-proposes-election-in-september-pm-govt-will-continue-until-war-goals-are-achieved/0000018e-a53b-df61-a1ef-ef7be5b20000</guid></item><item><title>威斯康星州的亲巴勒斯坦抗议投票对拜登来说是坏消息吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-03/ty-article/.highlight/was-wisconsins-pro-palestinian-protest-vote-bad-news-for-biden/0000018e-a4ea-dfed-ad9f-aefbf8130000</link><description>虽然威斯康星州并没有证明对拜登竞选来说是最糟糕的情况，但其他初选州（尽管不是摇摆州）的进步选民表达了他们对白宫针对加沙战争的以色列政策的不满</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-03/ty-article/.highlight/was-wisconsins-pro-palestinian-protest-vote-bad-news-for-biden/0000018e-a4ea-dfed-ad9f-aefbf8130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为杀害援助人员而付出政治代价——当他们不是巴勒斯坦人时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-a-political-price-for-killing-aid-workers-when-theyre-not-palestinians/0000018e-a43f-d24a-abbf-ee3f93d20000</link><description>造成世界中央厨房七名志愿者死亡的袭击是以色列对加沙人道主义援助系统的最新袭击。这次死者大多是西方人，以色列的打击行动将很难</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-pays-a-political-price-for-killing-aid-workers-when-theyre-not-palestinians/0000018e-a43f-d24a-abbf-ee3f93d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列竞争管理局将调查以色列航空公司在加沙战争期间的高票价问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-competition-authority-to-probe-el-al-for-high-airfares-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-a4a7-dd6b-abae-f7e79f1d0000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，大多数外国航空公司暂停飞往以色列的航班，以色列航空的机票价格飙升，主要是飞往美国和欧洲的航班。该航空公司 2023 年第四季度利润同比增长 367%</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 16:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-competition-authority-to-probe-el-al-for-high-airfares-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-a4a7-dd6b-abae-f7e79f1d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 180 天：波兰因涉嫌谋杀而调查援助人员被杀事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-180-poland-to-probe-aid-workers-killing-on-suspicion-of-murder/0000018e-a4bc-dd6b-abae-f7ff675f0001</link><description>波兰表示将调查一名世界中央厨房援助人员因涉嫌谋杀而被杀的事件 ■ 国防部长加兰特：以色列不希望与黎巴嫩发生战争，这“将是一个艰难的挑战” ■ 最新的人质释放/停火提议哈马斯消息人士称，前几轮谈判中止谈判的任何核心问题都没有取得突破 ■ 以下是战争结束 180 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 16:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-180-poland-to-probe-aid-workers-killing-on-suspicion-of-murder/0000018e-a4bc-dd6b-abae-f7ff675f0001</guid></item><item><title>无安全背景的本-格维尔提名人被批准担任国家安全部总干事； AG要求澄清</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-nominee-with-no-security-background-next-natl-security-ministry-director-general/0000018e-a419-d24a-abbf-ee39fcfe0000</link><description>拉斐尔·恩格尔提交了一封警察局长的信函后，公务员委员会批准了对他的任命，据说恩格尔在担任本杰明委员会副主席期间曾处理过安全问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:53:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-nominee-with-no-security-background-next-natl-security-ministry-director-general/0000018e-a419-d24a-abbf-ee39fcfe0000</guid></item><item><title>先是战争，然后是吞并：以色列准备永久占领加沙吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/war-first-then-annexation-is-israel-preparing-to-permanently-occupy-gaza/0000018e-a36f-d24a-abbf-ef6f5ae50000</link><description>尽管人们越来越期待汹涌的抗议活动可能会推翻内塔尼亚胡政府，但充满《圣经》的当权民族主义者正在按照以色列老套的做法，巩固重新安置加沙的计划。谁或什么可以阻止他们？</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:15:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/war-first-then-annexation-is-israel-preparing-to-permanently-occupy-gaza/0000018e-a36f-d24a-abbf-ef6f5ae50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家审计长称用于升级内塔尼亚胡住宅的资金是“可耻的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-comptroller-calls-funds-spent-to-upgrade-netanyahus-homes-scandalous/0000018e-a3f2-dd6b-abae-f7f379cb0000</link><description>马塔尼亚胡·恩格曼的报告审查了政府在前三任总理私人住宅的安全和维护方面所花费的资金，同时贝尔福官方官邸正在翻修。内塔尼亚胡的住宅在五年内花费了 2700 万谢克尔（720 万美元）</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 13:44:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-comptroller-calls-funds-spent-to-upgrade-netanyahus-homes-scandalous/0000018e-a3f2-dd6b-abae-f7f379cb0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的忠诚者声称抗议者危及他的生命，辛贝特和甘茨警告暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-loyalists-say-protesters-endangered-his-life-as-shin-bet-gantz-warn-of-violence/0000018e-a3b2-d24a-abbf-efbbc3f50000</link><description>以色列政治领导人和安全官员对周二在耶路撒冷举行的大规模反政府抗议活动做出了广泛的反应，社交媒体上出现了记录警察和抗议者之间暴力冲突的视频。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 13:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-loyalists-say-protesters-endangered-his-life-as-shin-bet-gantz-warn-of-violence/0000018e-a3b2-d24a-abbf-efbbc3f50000</guid></item><item><title>主厨何塞·安德烈斯现在能否决定以色列加沙战争的进程？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/could-chef-jose-andres-now-shape-the-course-of-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018e-a320-d9c2-afbe-abf6b2bd0000</link><description>以色列对世界中央厨房援助车队的致命袭击不仅是残酷战争中的又一起不幸悲剧。耶路撒冷和华盛顿的政策制定者请注意：这些死亡将对以色列针对哈马斯的战争产生战略性和直接的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 12:40:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/could-chef-jose-andres-now-shape-the-course-of-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018e-a320-d9c2-afbe-abf6b2bd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙杀害世界中央厨房援助人员会成为拜登的转折点吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/will-israels-killing-of-world-central-kitchen-aid-workers-be-the-tipping-point-for-biden/0000018e-a348-d9c2-afbe-abde6d8f0000</link><description>直到周一，拜登政府才甘愿为加沙严峻的人道主义局势提供“思考和祈祷”。以色列国防军“无意杀害”何塞·安德烈斯慈善机构的七名援助人员可能最终会造成数千名其他平民死亡无法做到的事情</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 12:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/will-israels-killing-of-world-central-kitchen-aid-workers-be-the-tipping-point-for-biden/0000018e-a348-d9c2-afbe-abde6d8f0000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列工党政客将领导改革运动拉比培训中心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/former-labor-party-politician-to-head-reform-movements-rabbinical-training-center/0000018e-a322-d9c2-afbe-abf688e20000</link><description>希伯来联合学院 - 犹太宗教学院任命了以色列改革拉比，该学院任命了纳赫曼·沙伊（Nachman Shai），他也是军队发言人和记者</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 12:19:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/former-labor-party-politician-to-head-reform-movements-rabbinical-training-center/0000018e-a322-d9c2-afbe-abf688e20000</guid></item><item><title>解救以色列人质并在纽约大型集会上发表讲话，纪念 10 月 7 日六周年纪念日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/rescued-hostage-to-address-major-n-y-rally-to-mark-six-month-anniversary-of-october-7/0000018e-a38c-dadc-a7af-fbafd4370000</link><description>来自各个政治和宗教领域的犹太机构和组织将聚集在联合国总部外参加大规模集会。由于犹太人在这个问题上达成了一致共识，组织者能够确保议程相互冲突的团体参与</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 11:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/rescued-hostage-to-address-major-n-y-rally-to-mark-six-month-anniversary-of-october-7/0000018e-a38c-dadc-a7af-fbafd4370000</guid></item><item><title>为什么最近的反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动尚未成为群众运动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/whats-preventing-the-latest-anti-netanyahu-protests-from-becoming-massive/0000018e-9fc1-d4c8-adce-fff5d9000000</link><description>尽管大多数以色列人对内塔尼亚胡没有信心，但四年来针对他和他的政府的第三波抗议活动尚未看到数十万人走上街头。这不仅是因为总理仍在设法引导有关加沙战争的公开辩论</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/whats-preventing-the-latest-anti-netanyahu-protests-from-becoming-massive/0000018e-9fc1-d4c8-adce-fff5d9000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方考虑对参与人质、反政府抗议活动的议员进行刑事调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/police-mulls-criminal-investigation-of-lawmaker-for-participating-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-a367-df93-a9af-b77f70340000</link><description>警方称，MK Naama Lazimi 被拍到在周六举行的示威活动中纵火。 “我建议警方调查那些故意阻止人质交易并让他们（哈马斯）慢慢杀害我们 134 名俘虏的人。 Ben-Gvir - 我不怕你，”她说</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:46:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/police-mulls-criminal-investigation-of-lawmaker-for-participating-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-a367-df93-a9af-b77f70340000</guid></item><item><title>揭开“加沙”这个名字的由来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/unraveling-the-origins-of-the-name-gaza/0000018e-a33c-ded0-a18f-e3fc704f0000</link><description>加沙是一座历史悠久的城市，自始至终它都有过不同的名字。穿越时间的语言之旅可能会带来意想不到的词源</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 09:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/unraveling-the-origins-of-the-name-gaza/0000018e-a33c-ded0-a18f-e3fc704f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院裁定不得释放受制裁寡头罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇的资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/top-court-rules-against-releasing-sanctioned-oligarch-roman-abramovichs-funds/0000018e-a2e0-d9c2-afbe-aaf6ef430000</link><description>该裁决推翻了法院此前向该银行发出的命令，要求该银行将罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇的 800 万谢克尔捐款转移给 ZAKA 搜救组织。该裁决指出，尽管受到制裁，但批准这笔捐赠将“使银行面临各种风险”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 08:48:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/top-court-rules-against-releasing-sanctioned-oligarch-roman-abramovichs-funds/0000018e-a2e0-d9c2-afbe-aaf6ef430000</guid></item></channel></rss>